name: Bullets with wings
description:
Forget violence and fly over frivolous things.  Printed on white card stock and relevant for all occasions.

4.375" x 5.75", complete with an envelope.

10% of the profit received from this card will be donated to the San Francisco Food Bank, in order to help homeless people in the Bay Area.
